<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="care-for">care for</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>照看；照顾</strong></h4>
<p>(take care of / look after)：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My dear father, you brought me into this world, you cared for me and loved me.
亲爱的父亲，您把我带到了这个世界上，照顾我，疼爱我。</p><footer>人教⑩ – 2</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>非常喜欢：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I think George <strong>doesn’t</strong> really <strong>care for</strong> TV plays.
我以为乔治不怎么喜欢电视剧。</p></div></div>